7
00:00:44,330 --> 00:00:46,051
I started out as a social worker.

8
00:00:46,611 --> 00:00:52,174
I did, I worked with adolescents with severe emotional and behavioral disturbances.

9
00:00:53,275 --> 00:00:56,597
And then after a while I felt a little bit burned out about that.

10
00:00:57,237 --> 00:01:00,979
Significantly because I hated talking on the telephone, which I've later discovered is

11
00:01:01,019 --> 00:01:06,362
common in our world, but at the time people thought it was a little flaky, so I moved

12
