00:34:38,131 --> 00:34:39,251
to say I kind of admire.

506
00:34:40,932 --> 00:34:42,593
Americans are more or less in the middle.

507
00:34:44,429 --> 00:34:48,672
We're accustomed to some consumer protections, but not as many as folks in the EU.

508
00:34:50,052 --> 00:34:57,736
We expect merchants and customers to be self-interested, but we also have a belief that self-interest

509
00:34:57,756 --> 00:35:04,140
can include the development of a long-term relationship that's going to be mutually beneficial.

510
00:35:06,901 --> 00:35:12,244
